leukapp.apps.workflows.constants module¶

This module contains the app constants. Information that isn’t likely to change and that is used across and leukapp should be stored here.

Important

DO NOT change any constant unless you know what you are doing.

APP_NAME = 'workflows'¶

Application’s name.

WORKFLOW_CREATE_URL = 'workflows:create'¶

Create URL reverse string.

WORKFLOW_LIST_URL = 'workflows:list'¶

List URL reverse string.

Fields required to create a new instance.

WORKFLOW_UPDATE_FIELDS = ()¶

Enabled fields to update an existing instance.

WORKFLOW_UNIQUE_TOGETHER = ('extraction', 'sequencing_center', 'ext_id')¶

Fields that are required to be unique together.
